headline: Where Will AMD Stock Be in 3 Years?
summary: The past three years have been forgettable for Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD) investors.  Shares of the chipmaker have declined 5% during this period, while the PHLX Semiconductor Sector index has recorded impressive gains of 36%.  The chipmaker has missed the artificial intelligence (AI) gravy train thus far.
